        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This hooded cloak is lined with rough foliage, vines, and bark that never wilts or rots away. When wearing this cloak, you gain a +1 item bonus to Stealth checks when in heavily forested areas.",
